---
title: Ruby Retreat 2025
description: "Ruby Retreat is a full weekend retreat for people interested in web development to gather and be awesome together. People attend for a variety of reasons: socializing, hacking, learning, teaching, gaming, and more."
url: https://retreat.ruby.org.au
image: https://retreat.ruby.org.au/images/social.jpg
---

<!-- Hero Section with Left Logo Layout -->
<section class="bg-[url('/images/cover.png')] bg-cover bg-center min-h-[22rem] text-center">
  <div class="container mx-auto mt-0 pt-16 pb-40 h-full">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8h-full">
      <!-- Left side: Logo and event details angled -->
      <div class="flex">
        <img src='/images/logo.png' class='h-64 block'>

        <div class="ml-6 xl:ml-12 flex-1 lg:flex-initial">
          <div class="">
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2 mt-6">
              Ruby Retreat 2025
            </h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-emerald-800 font-semibold">
              October 17-20th, 2025
            </p>
            <p class="text-base md:text-xl text-emerald-800">
              Warra Gnan Coastal Camp<br>
              Warrnambool, VIC
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right side: Blurb -->
      <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="bg-emerald-100/90 p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg mt-6 lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-md">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-3">Join Us for an Amazing Weekend</h2>
          <p class="text-emerald-800 mb-4">
            Ruby Retreat is a full weekend retreat for people interested in web development to gather and be awesome
            together. People attend for a variety of reasons: socializing, hacking, learning, teaching, gaming, and
            more. Though there is a focus on Ruby, we welcome anyone interested in programming or web technologies to
            join us.
          </p>
          <a class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300" id="buy_ticket" target="_blank" href="<%= ticket_url %>">
            Get your ticket →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

